</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-97_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-98_ pf-text-1"><strong>For parents and caregivers</strong> - Engage in certified paediatric first aid courses. Refresh your skills bi-annually.













</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-100_ pf-text-1"><strong>For schools and childcare providers</strong> - Ensure compliance with statutory requirements and conduct regular safety audits.
















